## Part 5: 디자인 토큰 상세

## Tailwind 프리셋 매핑

**colors:** `primary`, `secondary`, `tertiary`, `surface`, `text`, `success`, `error`, `warning`, `info`, `muted`, `border`, `focus`
**spacing:** `xs` ~ `block`, 0~32
**borderRadius:** `none`, `sm`, `base`, `md`, `lg`, `xl`, `full`, `control`, `card`, `modal`
**boxShadow:** `none`, `sm`, `base`, `md`, `lg`, `xl`, `card`, `card-hover`, `modal`, `dropdown`, `focus`
**fontSize:** `Xs` ~ `4xl`, `control-sm/md/lg`
**zIndex:** `base`, `raised`, `dropdown`, `modal`, `tooltip`
**transitionDuration:** `fast`, `normal`, `slow`, `interactive`, `content`
**height/minHeight:** `control-sm`, `control-md`, `control-lg`
**opacity:** `disabled`, `muted`, `hover`, `overlay`

